        With QuickClean, you get high-quality service without breaking the bank. Our pricing is simple and transparent – no hidden fees, no surprise charges. Whether it’s a single item or a full laundry load, you’ll always know what to <expect class="br"></expect>
        <expect class="br"></expect>
        
        Fast Turnaround Time
        Need your clothes cleaned in a hurry? We offer same-day or next-day laundry services to ensure you’re always ready for your busy schedule.</h3>
</section>
    <div class="container mt-5">
       

        <!-- Listings Table -->
        <h1>Service Provided by us</h1>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Services</th>
                    <th>Description</th>
                    <th>Price</th>
                    <th>Location</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <% allListings.forEach(function(listing) { %>
                    <tr>
                        <td><%= listing.title %></td>
                        <td><%= listing.description %></td>
                        <td><%= new Intl.NumberFormat('en-IN', { style: 'currency', currency: 'INR' }).format(listing.price) %></td>
                        <td><%= listing.location %></td>
                    </tr>
                <% }); %>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    <footer style="background-image: url('images/dry6.png'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; padding: 40px 0; color: white;">
        <p>QuickClean - Your Trusted Laundry Service</p>
        <a href="/contact-list">Contact Us</a>
    </footer>
    

    <!-- Bootstrap JS for any future interactive features (optional) -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
